ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>
[There have been prior reports of food-borne viral gastroenteritis
outbreaks due to Norwalk-like viruses. An epidemiologic investigation of
this suspected food-borne outbreak should clarify if there is a real
outbreak and the possible or probable etiology as well as route of
transmission (common source and/or person-to-person). From the information
given in this article, there does appear to be an increase in school
absences on Monday and Tuesday by absolute numbers presented which may have
begun on Friday, the day following the suspected exposure. ProMED-mail
would like to receive more information on this before venturing further
speculation. - Mod.MPP
